00:38:33,619 --> 00:38:35,860
[SPEAKER_00] A ime ostali su

1038
00:38:35,860 --> 00:38:36,659
[SPEAKER_00] zapomčili imena

1039
00:38:36,659 --> 00:38:37,900
[SPEAKER_00] samo onih zloglasnih.

1040
00:38:37,900 --> 00:38:39,159
[SPEAKER_00] Pilat,

1041
00:38:39,159 --> 00:38:39,860
[SPEAKER_00] po čemu je znao?

1042
00:38:39,860 --> 00:38:41,980
[SPEAKER_00] Samo po negativnom događaju

1043
00:38:41,980 --> 00:38:42,500
[SPEAKER_00] koju činio.

1044
00:38:42,980 --> 00:38:43,420
[SPEAKER_00] kajfa.

1045
00:38:43,420 --> 00:38:50,340
[SPEAKER_00] Sveti Franjo,

1046
00:38:50,340 --> 00:38:51,780
[SPEAKER_00] Salešk je slično stvar,

1047
00:38:51,780 --> 00:38:52,059
[SPEAKER_00] rekao,

1048
00:38:52,059 --> 00:38:53,679
[SPEAKER_00] svatite gdje ste posađeni.

1049
00:38:53,679 --> 00:38:58,239
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno da se sad pitate

1050
00:38:58,239 --> 00:38:59,460
[SPEAKER_00] šta ako ti,

1051
00:38:59,460 --> 00:39:01,739
[SPEAKER_00] naši crkveni autoriteti,

1052
00:39:01,739 --> 00:39:05,420
[SPEAKER_00] su pokvareni.

1053
00:39:05,420 --> 00:39:07,400
[SPEAKER_00] Šta ako taj svećenik,

1054
00:39:07,400 --> 00:39:08,300
[SPEAKER_00] šta ako taj vojitelj,

1055
00:39:08,300 --> 00:39:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] zajedni sa stvarima krive motive,

1056
00:39:10,000 --> 00:39:11,900
[SPEAKER_00] i ako čini zlo.

1057
00:39:12,980 --> 00:39:14,059
[SPEAKER_00] Jel to znači

1058
00:39:14,059 --> 00:39:15,679
[SPEAKER_00] da ga ja trebam častiti?

1059
00:39:15,679 --> 00:39:16,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ja vam kažem da.

1060
00:39:16,599 --> 00:39:19,300
[SPEAKER_00] Evo pogledajte primjer

1061
00:39:19,300 --> 00:39:21,139
[SPEAKER_00] Ane i Elija.

1062
00:39:21,139 --> 00:39:23,639
[SPEAKER_00] Ana je majka Samuelova,

1063
00:39:23,639 --> 00:39:24,820
[SPEAKER_00] nije mogla dobiti djete.

1064
00:39:24,820 --> 00:39:26,619
[SPEAKER_00] I bila je u muci,

1065
00:39:26,619 --> 00:39:27,139
[SPEAKER_00] jer joj se

1066
00:39:27,139 --> 00:39:29,840
[SPEAKER_00] druga žena njenog muža

1067
00:39:29,840 --> 00:39:31,699
[SPEAKER_00] toliko joj se rugala,

1068
00:39:31,699 --> 00:39:33,300
[SPEAKER_00] toliko joj ponižavala

1069
00:39:33,300 --> 00:39:34,440
[SPEAKER_00] zbog toga što ona ne može

1070
00:39:34,440 --> 00:39:34,960
[SPEAKER_00] dobiti djete,

1071
00:39:34,960 --> 00:39:36,360
[SPEAKER_00] da je bila jadna i nikakva.

1072
00:39:36,360 --> 00:39:38,940
[SPEAKER_00] I kada je došla u hram,

1073
00:39:38,940 --> 00:39:41,019
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno u hram,

1074
00:39:41,539 --> 00:39:43,119
[SPEAKER_00] kad su prinosili žrtve,

1075
00:39:43,119 --> 00:39:45,300
[SPEAKER_00] Elija je tad bio svećenik,

1076
00:39:45,300 --> 00:39:46,239
[SPEAKER_00] veliki svećenik,

1077
00:39:46,239 --> 00:39:47,480
[SPEAKER_00] koji je bio pokvaren lik.

1078
00:39:47,480 --> 00:39:49,280
[SPEAKER_00] Pustio da njegovi sinovi

1079
00:39:49,280 --> 00:39:52,460
[SPEAKER_00] bludniče sa hramskim djevojkama,

1080
00:39:52,460 --> 00:39:54,400
[SPEAKER_00] koje su čuvale šator.

1081
00:39:55,500 --> 00:39:57,639
[SPEAKER_00] Pustio ih je da kradu od žrtava

1082
00:39:57,639 --> 00:40:00,840
[SPEAKER_00] koje su ljudi prinosili Bogu.

1083
00:40:00,840 --> 00:40:02,139
[SPEAKER_00] Jer mu je pasalo,

1084
00:40:02,139 --> 00:40:03,199
[SPEAKER_00] jer je on dobio dio.

1085
00:40:03,199 --> 00:40:06,059
[SPEAKER_00] I ona je plakala, ridala,

1086
00:40:06,059 --> 00:40:07,980
[SPEAKER_00] molila Boga

1087
00:40:07,980 --> 00:40:09,639
[SPEAKER_00] i šapčeći

1088
00:40:09,639 --> 00:40:12,199
[SPEAKER_00] prikazivala svoju molitvu.

1089
00:40:12,199 --> 00:40:13,599
[SPEAKER_00] I kad je to vidio Eli,

1090
00:40:13,599 --> 00:40:13,960
[SPEAKER_00] rekao je,

1091
00:40:13,960 --> 00:40:14,679
[SPEAKER_00] šta si pijan?

1092
00:40:14,679 --> 00:40:15,739
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde, otrezni se više.

1093
00:40:15,739 --> 00:40:17,840
[SPEAKER_00] Zamislite da danas vi dođete

1094
00:40:17,840 --> 00:40:18,840
[SPEAKER_00] u tu situaciju,

1095
00:40:18,900 --> 00:40:19,840
[SPEAKER_00] dođem svećenik,

1096
00:40:19,840 --> 00:40:20,320
[SPEAKER_00] ili bojite,

1097
00:40:20,320 --> 00:40:21,179
[SPEAKER_00] šta si pijan?

1098
00:40:21,179 --> 00:40:22,500
[SPEAKER_00] A ti izljevaš dušu.

1099
00:40:22,500 --> 00:40:23,619
[SPEAKER_00] Pa poludili bi,

1100
00:40:23,619 --> 00:40:24,500
[SPEAKER_00] idem u drugu crku,

1101
00:40:24,500 --> 00:40:25,780
[SPEAKER_00] neće ti tu više nikad doći.

1102
00:40:25,780 --> 00:40:29,900
[SPEAKER_00] Kakav si ti to svećenik?

1103
00:40:29,900 --> 00:40:31,280
[SPEAKER_00] T, t, t, t, t, t, t, t, t.

1104
00:40:31,280 --> 00:40:32,880
[SPEAKER_00] A šta mu ona rekla?

1105
00:40:32,880 --> 00:40:33,619
[SPEAKER_00] Gospodaru.

1106
00:40:33,619 --> 00:40:36,380
[SPEAKER_00] Jadna sam i nevoljna

1107
00:40:36,380 --> 00:40:37,199
[SPEAKER_00] i tako dalje.

1108
00:40:37,199 --> 00:40:39,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ne sudi me krivo,

1109
00:40:39,539 --> 00:40:40,400
[SPEAKER_00] ali gospodaru.

1110
00:40:40,400 --> 00:40:43,900
[SPEAKER_00] I šta je on kaže?

1111
00:40:43,900 --> 00:40:46,900
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, nek ti Jahve usliši.

1112
00:40:48,659 --> 00:40:49,360
[SPEAKER_00] Ona ga je častila,

1113
00:40:49,360 --> 00:40:50,559
[SPEAKER_00] ne zato što je bio pokvarin

1114
00:40:50,559 --> 00:40:52,780
[SPEAKER_00] i zato što je bio svet.

1115
00:40:52,780 --> 00:40:54,340
[SPEAKER_00] Nije bio ni svet,

1116
00:40:54,340 --> 00:40:56,260
[SPEAKER_00] niti joj dobro pristupio,

1117
00:40:56,260 --> 00:40:58,119
[SPEAKER_00] ali ga je počastila.

1118
00:40:58,119 --> 00:40:59,880
[SPEAKER_00] Jel je bio duhovni autoritet.

1119
00:40:59,880 --> 00:41:01,579
[SPEAKER_00] I molitve su uslišane.

1120
00:41:01,579 --> 00:41:04,039
[SPEAKER_00] Možeš bolji primjer Davida

1121
00:41:04,039 --> 00:41:05,679
[SPEAKER_00] i Šaula.

1122
00:41:05,679 --> 00:41:09,260
[SPEAKER_00] Kad je neko bio pomazan

1123
00:41:09,260 --> 00:41:09,920
[SPEAKER_00] tad za kralja,

1124
00:41:09,920 --> 00:41:11,639
[SPEAKER_00] on je imao vlast veliku.

1125
00:41:11,639 --> 00:41:16,179
[SPEAKER_00] I David,

1126
00:41:18,420 --> 00:41:20,519
[SPEAKER_00] kako je rastao,

1127
00:41:20,519 --> 00:41:21,480
[SPEAKER_00] rastao svetosti,

1128
00:41:21,480 --> 00:41:22,760
[SPEAKER_00] vježbao svoj gospodinu,

1129
00:41:22,760 --> 00:41:23,440
[SPEAKER_00] postoje,

1130
00:41:23,440 --> 00:41:24,639
[SPEAKER_00] oslobodio je,

1131
00:41:24,639 --> 00:41:25,219
[SPEAKER_00] imao je onu

1132
00:41:25,219 --> 00:41:28,099
[SPEAKER_00] zgodu sa Filistejcem,

1133
00:41:28,099 --> 00:41:29,960
[SPEAKER_00] počeo je ići u ratne pohode

1134
00:41:29,960 --> 00:41:30,880
[SPEAKER_00] i bio jako uspješan.

1135
00:41:30,880 --> 00:41:31,659
[SPEAKER_00] Onda su djevojke,

1136
00:41:31,659 --> 00:41:32,340
[SPEAKER_00] žene pjevale,

1137
00:41:32,340 --> 00:41:33,739
[SPEAKER_00] Šaul pobi tisuće,

1138
00:41:33,739 --> 00:41:35,079
[SPEAKER_00] David desetke tisuća.

1139
00:41:35,079 --> 00:41:36,719
[SPEAKER_00] I Šaulu se to nije svidilo,

1140
00:41:36,719 --> 00:41:37,599
[SPEAKER_00] ali on je bio kralj.

1141
00:41:37,599 --> 00:41:39,960
[SPEAKER_00] I pobojao se za svoje kraljevstvo,

1142
00:41:39,960 --> 00:41:41,980
[SPEAKER_00] da će mu David preuzeti.

1143
00:41:43,420 --> 00:41:44,940
[SPEAKER_00] Zavist ušla u njegov srce,

1144
00:41:44,940 --> 00:41:46,199
[SPEAKER_00] mržnja

1145
00:41:46,199 --> 00:41:48,139
[SPEAKER_00] i želja da ga ubije.

1146
00:41:48,139 --> 00:41:51,079
[SPEAKER_00] Dva put je pokušao ga ubijet dok mu je sviro

1147
00:41:51,079 --> 00:41:53,559
[SPEAKER_00] i treći put

1148
00:41:53,559 --> 00:41:56,019
[SPEAKER_00] kad je pozvao na gozbu,

1149
00:41:56,019 --> 00:41:57,960
[SPEAKER_00] onda je David to prepozno,

1150
00:41:57,960 --> 00:42:00,519
[SPEAKER_00] Jonathan mu javio da ga ovaj stvarno želi ubiti

1151
00:42:00,519 --> 00:42:02,659
[SPEAKER_00] i David odlazi u bijeg.

1152
00:42:04,440 --> 00:42:06,280
[SPEAKER_00] Njemu se priključuju svi nesvrstani,

1153
00:42:06,280 --> 00:42:10,099
[SPEAKER_00] svi koji nisu zadovoljni,

1154
00:42:10,099 --> 00:42:12,159
[SPEAKER_00] pljačkaši i sl.

1155
00:42:12,159 --> 00:42:16,159
[SPEAKER_00] I on postaje njihov vođa.

1156
00:42:16,159 --> 00:42:20,840
[SPEAKER_00] I Šaul iznova, iznova pokušao obijet Davida.

1157
00:42:20,840 --> 00:42:24,059
[SPEAKER_00] I jedne prilike da ga lovia po tim špiljama,

1158
00:42:24,059 --> 00:42:26,820
[SPEAKER_00] oni su se sakrali u jednu duboku špilju,

1159
00:42:26,820 --> 00:42:30,539
[SPEAKER_00] a kaže sve to pismo da je Šaul došao čučnut.

1160
00:42:31,320 --> 00:42:36,559
[SPEAKER_00] Što znači došao je obavit fiziološke potrebe.

1161
00:42:36,559 --> 00:42:39,079
[SPEAKER_00] I dok je on to radio,

1162
00:42:39,079 --> 00:42:40,820
[SPEAKER_00] rekli su Davidovi,

1163
00:42:40,820 --> 00:42:42,500
[SPEAKER_00] sad ti je Bog dao,

1164
00:42:42,500 --> 00:42:44,179
[SPEAKER_00] dao ti je predotigao na platnju,

1165
00:42:44,179 --> 00:42:45,340
[SPEAKER_00] onaj koji tebe hoće ubit,

1166
00:42:45,340 --> 00:42:46,739
[SPEAKER_00] sad ti imaš priliku.

1167
00:42:46,739 --> 00:42:50,159
[SPEAKER_00] I Šaul se zamislio.

1168
00:42:50,159 --> 00:42:54,360
[SPEAKER_00] A onda ga je opekla save što je to zamislio

1169
00:42:54,360 --> 00:42:57,280
[SPEAKER_00] i rekao je svojima ukorio ih je,

1170
00:42:57,280 --> 00:42:58,539
[SPEAKER_00] on je pomazanik.

1171
00:43:01,320 --> 00:43:04,559
[SPEAKER_00] On je od gospodina.

1172
00:43:04,559 --> 00:43:07,900
[SPEAKER_00] On je moj autoritet.

1173
00:43:07,900 --> 00:43:09,599
[SPEAKER_00] I otišao,

1174
00:43:09,599 --> 00:43:11,500
[SPEAKER_00] ocijeko mu je skut haljine.

1175
00:43:11,500 --> 00:43:15,199
[SPEAKER_00] I kasnije kad je Šaul izašao,

1176
00:43:15,199 --> 00:43:16,320
[SPEAKER_00] David mu je pokazao.

1177
00:43:17,679 --> 00:43:19,900
[SPEAKER_00] I rekao je li ja imam krivnje?

1178
00:43:19,900 --> 00:43:22,980
[SPEAKER_00] Vidiš da sam te imao u svojim rukama,

1179
00:43:22,980 --> 00:43:24,119
[SPEAKER_00] što sam ti zlo učinio?

1180
00:43:24,119 --> 00:43:25,539
[SPEAKER_00] I tu se Šaul pokajo.

1181
00:43:25,539 --> 00:43:27,139
[SPEAKER_00] I rekao,

1182
00:43:27,139 --> 00:43:30,199
[SPEAKER_00] ti si postupio sve to,

1183
00:43:30,199 --> 00:43:31,480
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam kriv što te idem ubit.

1184
00:43:33,059 --> 00:43:35,940
[SPEAKER_00] I vratio ga i postavio ga ponovno u službu,

1185
00:43:35,940 --> 00:43:38,440
[SPEAKER_00] ali nakon nekog vremena opet isto stvar.

1186
00:43:38,440 --> 00:43:39,119
[SPEAKER_00] Zavis,

1187
00:43:39,119 --> 00:43:40,280
[SPEAKER_00] taj, taj, taj, ponovno.

1188
00:43:40,280 --> 00:43:41,739
[SPEAKER_00] I David

1189
00:43:41,739 --> 00:43:44,760
[SPEAKER_00] ga je imao još jednom

1190
00:43:44,760 --> 00:43:46,159
[SPEAKER_00] u rukama,

1191
00:43:46,159 --> 00:43:48,300
[SPEAKER_00] kad je tvrd san pao na

1192
00:43:48,300 --> 00:43:50,400
[SPEAKER_00] Šaula i njegove ljude.

1193
00:43:50,400 --> 00:43:52,480
[SPEAKER_00] I oni su došli,

1194
00:43:52,480 --> 00:43:55,039
[SPEAKER_00] po noći u njegov šator,

1195
00:43:55,039 --> 00:43:57,960
[SPEAKER_00] njegov vojskovoća.

1196
00:43:58,659 --> 00:44:00,460
[SPEAKER_00] Davidov prvi mu je rekao,

1197
00:44:00,460 --> 00:44:01,340
[SPEAKER_00] sad ga imaš.

1198
00:44:01,340 --> 00:44:04,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ali David je ostao čvrst.

1199
00:44:04,099 --> 00:44:05,480
[SPEAKER_00] To je bila zadnja kušnja.

1200
00:44:05,480 --> 00:44:08,099
[SPEAKER_00] A činilo se kao da mu je Bog to sve složio.

1201
00:44:08,099 --> 00:44:09,079
[SPEAKER_00] Gledaj, pao je tvrd san,

1202
00:44:09,079 --> 00:44:09,980
[SPEAKER_00] on je moj neprijatelj,

1203
00:44:09,980 --> 00:44:11,679
[SPEAKER_00] kvari izraelski narod.

1204
00:44:11,679 --> 00:44:15,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ne, neću dići ruku na pomazenika Boga,

1205
00:44:15,480 --> 00:44:16,960
[SPEAKER_00] živoga, Jahve.

1206
00:44:16,960 --> 00:44:20,099
[SPEAKER_00] I tu je David bio obilno nagrađen.

1207
00:44:20,099 --> 00:44:21,780
[SPEAKER_00] I znamo da je David

1208
00:44:21,780 --> 00:44:24,539
[SPEAKER_00] najpoznatiji kralj Izraela

1209
00:44:24,539 --> 00:44:25,559
[SPEAKER_00] poslije gospodina.

1210
00:44:27,380 --> 00:44:29,380
[SPEAKER_00] Čovjek po srcu Božje.

1211
00:44:29,380 --> 00:44:35,059
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da častit,

1212
00:44:35,059 --> 00:44:36,380
[SPEAKER_00] čak i onda

1213
00:44:36,380 --> 00:44:40,340
[SPEAKER_00] kad duhovni autoritet nije u pravu.

1214
00:44:40,340 --> 00:44:43,699
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ne častimo onoga

1215
00:44:43,699 --> 00:44:45,599
[SPEAKER_00] koji predstavlja taj autoritet,

1216
00:44:45,599 --> 00:44:47,300
[SPEAKER_00] nego onoga koji daje autoritet,

1217
00:44:47,300 --> 00:44:47,900
[SPEAKER_00] a to je Bog.

1218
00:44:47,900 --> 00:44:50,119
[SPEAKER_00] Samo Krista.

1219
00:44:50,119 --> 00:44:53,599
[SPEAKER_00] Sad bih prešao na drugi dio

1220
00:44:53,599 --> 00:44:54,900
[SPEAKER_00] koji je malo škakljivi,

1221
00:44:54,900 --> 00:44:56,360
[SPEAKER_00] to je državni voditelji.

1222
00:44:57,099 --> 00:44:59,199
[SPEAKER_00] jer su Plenković i Milanović,

1223
00:44:59,199 --> 00:45:01,380
[SPEAKER_00] naši političari.

1224
00:45:01,380 --> 00:45:05,739
[SPEAKER_00] Velika je kriza

1225
00:45:05,739 --> 00:45:10,119
[SPEAKER_00] i malo gdje se može čut

1226
00:45:10,119 --> 00:45:12,179
[SPEAKER_00] da će neko govorit ovako,

1227
00:45:12,179 --> 00:45:13,199
[SPEAKER_00] pa čak i u crkvi.

1228
00:45:13,199 --> 00:45:15,579
[SPEAKER_00] Jer mi Hrvati

1229
00:45:15,579 --> 00:45:17,039
[SPEAKER_00] imamo taj problem.

1230
00:45:17,039 --> 00:45:18,940
[SPEAKER_00] Mi uopće ne znamo

1231
00:45:18,940 --> 00:45:20,219
[SPEAKER_00] kako se časti vlast.

1232
00:45:21,059 --> 00:45:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Možda si možemo,

1233
00:45:22,000 --> 00:45:24,420
[SPEAKER_00] malo se možemo opravljati,

1234
00:45:24,420 --> 00:45:26,159
[SPEAKER_00] jer skoro tisuću godina

1235
00:45:26,159 --> 00:45:27,659
[SPEAKER_00] nismo imali svoju državu.

1236
00:45:27,659 --> 00:45:29,380
[SPEAKER_00] Od Zvonimira

1237
00:45:29,380 --> 00:45:31,139
[SPEAKER_00] i kogod je vladao nad nama,

1238
00:45:31,139 --> 00:45:34,079
[SPEAKER_00] on nas je tlačio i kraj od nas.

1239
00:45:34,079 --> 00:45:36,699
[SPEAKER_00] I nemamo to u sebi.

1240
00:45:36,699 --> 00:45:37,760
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znamo častiti,

1241
00:45:37,760 --> 00:45:38,480
[SPEAKER_00] oni su uvijek bili

1242
00:45:38,480 --> 00:45:40,179
[SPEAKER_00] kontra naroda.

1243
00:45:40,340 --> 00:45:40,960
[SPEAKER_00] niko nije radio

1244
00:45:40,960 --> 00:45:41,980
[SPEAKER_00] u interesu naroda.

1245
00:45:41,980 --> 00:45:49,619
[SPEAKER_00] I moram vam reći

1246
00:45:49,619 --> 00:45:50,300
[SPEAKER_00] da ipak

1247
00:45:50,300 --> 00:45:53,260
[SPEAKER_00] moramo častiti svoje državne.

1248
00:45:53,260 --> 00:45:56,199
[SPEAKER_00] Čak danas ja vidim

1249
00:45:56,199 --> 00:45:57,980
[SPEAKER_00] na našoj sceni

1250
00:45:57,980 --> 00:45:59,059
[SPEAKER_00] političare

1251
00:45:59,059 --> 00:46:01,139
[SPEAKER_00] koji se zovu katoličkim,

1252
00:46:01,139 --> 00:46:03,559
[SPEAKER_00] vidim i katoličke udruge

1253
00:46:03,559 --> 00:46:05,179
[SPEAKER_00] koje su aktivne u politici,

1254
00:46:05,179 --> 00:46:09,260
[SPEAKER_00] koji su prvi i prednjače

1255
00:46:09,260 --> 00:46:10,239
[SPEAKER_00] u kritiziranju,

1256
00:46:10,239 --> 00:46:11,800
[SPEAKER_00] postavljanju,

1257
00:46:11,800 --> 00:46:13,739
[SPEAKER_00] koji se postavlja superiorno

1258
00:46:13,739 --> 00:46:16,079
[SPEAKER_00] i malo me sram,

1259
00:46:16,079 --> 00:46:18,039
[SPEAKER_00] što se zovu katolički.

1260
00:46:18,039 --> 00:46:19,900
[SPEAKER_00] Jer to nije biblijski put.

1261
00:46:19,900 --> 00:46:22,059
[SPEAKER_00] To nije put katoličke crkve.

1262
00:46:22,059 --> 00:46:25,820
[SPEAKER_00] Rimljani 13.

1263
00:46:25,820 --> 00:46:38,559
[SPEAKER_00] Svaka duša neka se podlaže vlastima

1264
00:46:38,559 --> 00:46:40,320
[SPEAKER_00] nad sobom.

1265
00:46:40,320 --> 00:46:41,719
[SPEAKER_00] Jer nema vlasti

1266
00:46:41,719 --> 00:46:42,440
[SPEAKER_00] doli od Boga.

1267
00:46:42,440 --> 00:46:45,099
[SPEAKER_00] Koje postoje

1268
00:46:45,099 --> 00:46:46,679
[SPEAKER_00] od Boga su postavljane.

1269
00:46:46,679 --> 00:46:49,980
[SPEAKER_00] Stoga tko se suprostavlja

1270
00:46:49,980 --> 00:46:50,539
[SPEAKER_00] vlasti

1271
00:46:50,539 --> 00:46:51,719
[SPEAKER_00] Božjoj se

1272
00:46:51,719 --> 00:46:52,480
[SPEAKER_00] odredbi

1273
00:46:52,480 --> 00:46:53,260
[SPEAKER_00] protivi.

1274
00:46:53,260 --> 00:46:55,840
[SPEAKER_00] Jeste svjesni što ovdje kaže?

1275
00:46:55,840 --> 00:46:57,780
[SPEAKER_00] Plenković i Milanović su od Boga.

1276
00:46:59,840 --> 00:47:01,400
[SPEAKER_00] oni su postavljeni od Boga.

1277
00:47:03,880 --> 00:47:04,800
[SPEAKER_00] njih treba častiti.

1278
00:47:04,800 --> 00:47:06,639
[SPEAKER_00] Jesu li uvijek upravo?

1279
00:47:06,639 --> 00:47:06,980
[SPEAKER_00] Nisu.

1280
00:47:06,980 --> 00:47:11,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ali nam to ne daje pravo

1281
00:47:11,460 --> 00:47:12,320
[SPEAKER_00] da ih ne častimo.

1282
00:47:13,500 --> 00:47:14,920
[SPEAKER_00] Daću vam primjer jedne zajednice.

1283
00:47:14,920 --> 00:47:18,900
[SPEAKER_00] Jedne zajednice koja je stagnirala tri godine.

1284
00:47:18,900 --> 00:47:27,219
[SPEAKER_00] Vojitelj te zajednice više nije znao šta da učini, ali je primijetio jednu stvar.

1285
00:47:27,760 --> 00:47:32,679
[SPEAKER_00] Svi članovi njegove zajednice su opasno kritizirali državnu vlast,

1286
00:47:32,679 --> 00:47:38,099
[SPEAKER_00] mjesnu, ona kojim nabija poreze i mnogi nisu plaćali poreze.

1287
00:47:38,099 --> 00:47:45,900
[SPEAKER_00] I on ih je oštro, ali u ljubavi, poučio o ovom što piše u Rimljanima 13, cijeli tekst, napravio predavanje.

1288
00:47:45,900 --> 00:47:53,840
[SPEAKER_00] Otišo u mjesnu zajednicu i pito je tamo u općini koja je najveća potreba mjesne zajednice.

1289
00:47:53,840 --> 00:48:01,519
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su mu rekli, najveća potreba je vatrogascima posebne nekakve gas maske s kojima oni vide u dimu.

1290
00:48:01,519 --> 00:48:05,800
[SPEAKER_00] Jer najviše ljudi zapravo u požaru umre od dima, a ne od vatre.

1291
00:48:05,800 --> 00:48:09,340
[SPEAKER_00] Uguše se i njima te maske pomažu da spašave živote.

1292
00:48:09,340 --> 00:48:11,360
[SPEAKER_00] Oni se riskiraju i žrtvuju.

1293
00:48:11,360 --> 00:48:15,639
[SPEAKER_00] I nakon te teme koje mi je održao, rekao mi je danas skupljamo za te maske.

1294
00:48:15,639 --> 00:48:19,780
[SPEAKER_00] Jedna košta 25 tisuća dolara, to je u Americi bilo.

1295
00:48:19,780 --> 00:48:21,920
[SPEAKER_00] I oni su skupili za jednu masku.

1296
00:48:23,000 --> 00:48:35,480
[SPEAKER_00] I kad su organizirali poklon za tu ekipu, za gradsku zajednicu i sve čelnike, oni su se šokirali koliko ljudi zapravo iz vlasti došlo.

1297
00:48:36,820 --> 00:48:47,940
[SPEAKER_00] I kad je voditelj, ovako po Rimljanima 13, rekao da oni ovim činom žele zahvaliti na svemu što oni rade za njih i da ih smatraju Božim slugama,

1298
00:48:49,699 --> 00:48:51,059
[SPEAKER_00] ovi su bili oduševljeni.

1299
00:48:51,059 --> 00:48:56,800
[SPEAKER_00] Samo to su rekli, bez ikakve kritike, bez ikakve zamolbe da se nešto napravi.

1300
00:48:56,800 --> 00:48:58,340
[SPEAKER_00] Znate šta se dogodilo?

1301
00:48:58,340 --> 00:49:01,280
[SPEAKER_00] Neki od tih službenika,

1302
00:49:01,280 --> 00:49:04,019
[SPEAKER_00] vlasti su došli na susrete,

1303
00:49:04,019 --> 00:49:08,280
[SPEAKER_00] to se pročulo i oni su postali jedna ugledna zajednica

1304
00:49:08,280 --> 00:49:14,300
[SPEAKER_00] koja je sa sto članova počela organizirati konferencije za devetsto ljudi.

1305
00:49:14,300 --> 00:49:16,300
[SPEAKER_00] Devetsto vjernih su imali u zajednici.

1306
00:49:16,300 --> 00:49:18,400
[SPEAKER_00] I logično je, ljudi moji.

1307
00:49:18,400 --> 00:49:21,880
[SPEAKER_00] Jer oni su primili nagradu

1308
00:49:21,880 --> 00:49:24,920
[SPEAKER_00] jer su dali čast kome?

1309
00:49:24,920 --> 00:49:27,239
[SPEAKER_00] Društvenim voditeljima.

1310
00:49:27,239 --> 00:49:30,900
[SPEAKER_00] Prirodno je da je društveni voditelj čuvar,

1311
00:49:30,900 --> 00:49:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno ključar vrata grada, vrata mjesta,

1312
00:49:34,000 --> 00:49:37,820
[SPEAKER_00] vrata neke zajednice, općine, županije.

1313
00:49:39,019 --> 00:49:42,500
[SPEAKER_00] I ako se otvore ta vrata, otvaraju se vrata za sve te ljude.

1314
00:49:42,500 --> 00:49:46,460
[SPEAKER_00] A mi nemamo takvu kulturu.

1315
00:49:46,460 --> 00:49:48,380
[SPEAKER_00] I tu kulturu treba izgrađivati.

1316
00:49:48,380 --> 00:49:50,400
[SPEAKER_00] Čašćena voditelja.

1317
00:49:50,400 --> 00:49:54,780
[SPEAKER_00] Sad ćete me pitati,

1318
00:49:54,780 --> 00:49:58,480
[SPEAKER_00] je li to isključuje da ih treba opominjati

1319
00:49:58,480 --> 00:49:59,679
[SPEAKER_00] kad nešto loše rade? Ne.

1320
00:49:59,679 --> 00:50:02,239
[SPEAKER_00] Ali danas toga nema, ljudi moji.

1321
00:50:02,239 --> 00:50:06,599
[SPEAKER_00] Nema onog opominjanja kako smo čuli danas u Evanđelju.

1322
00:50:08,280 --> 00:50:10,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ivano pominje kralja Heroda.

1323
00:50:10,500 --> 00:50:14,619
[SPEAKER_00] Javno i otvoreno.

1324
00:50:14,619 --> 00:50:16,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ali u ljubavi.

1325
00:50:16,500 --> 00:50:17,739
[SPEAKER_00] Znate kako to znamo?

1326
00:50:17,739 --> 00:50:19,860
[SPEAKER_00] Jer kaže da ga je Herod poštovao,

1327
00:50:19,860 --> 00:50:23,460
[SPEAKER_00] volio ga slušat i često se našao zadivljen.

1328
00:50:26,500 --> 00:50:28,920
[SPEAKER_00] To ne gasi našu proročku službu.

1329
00:50:28,920 --> 00:50:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali naša proročka služba se ne može odraditi u kafiću,

1330
00:50:34,000 --> 00:50:35,880
[SPEAKER_00] na kavi i cigari,

1331
00:50:35,880 --> 00:50:39,500
[SPEAKER_00] ili doma kad ručeš sa svojima.

1332
00:50:39,500 --> 00:50:41,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ne može.

1333
00:50:41,340 --> 00:50:44,860
[SPEAKER_00] Ona se mora biti izrečena u ljubavi ako si pozvan.

1334
00:50:44,860 --> 00:50:47,440
[SPEAKER_00] Onome koma treba riječ poslati.

1335
00:50:47,820 --> 00:50:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Koji vam je jako dobar primjer?

1336
00:50:49,000 --> 00:50:50,780
[SPEAKER_00] Samuel i Šaul.

1337
00:50:50,780 --> 00:50:51,780
[SPEAKER_00] Samuel prorok,

1338
00:50:51,780 --> 00:50:54,159
[SPEAKER_00] kojeg je Bog podigo,

1339
00:50:54,159 --> 00:50:55,199
[SPEAKER_00] kojeg je Bog volio.

1340
00:50:55,199 --> 00:50:58,639
[SPEAKER_00] Kad je Šaul otvoreno

1341
00:50:58,639 --> 00:51:03,460
[SPEAKER_00] i drsko,

1342
00:51:03,460 --> 00:51:06,380
[SPEAKER_00] nepoštivo ono što mu je Bog rekao da napravi.

1343
00:51:06,380 --> 00:51:09,280
[SPEAKER_00] Napravi kleto uništenje nad Amalećanima.

1344
00:51:09,280 --> 00:51:11,800
[SPEAKER_00] On je zadržao najbolju stoku zbog naroda.

1345
00:51:14,820 --> 00:51:16,840
[SPEAKER_00] Šaul dobio od gospodina proročku riječ za njega

1346
00:51:16,840 --> 00:51:19,860
[SPEAKER_00] da se gospodin pokaju što ga je postavio za kralja.

1347
00:51:19,860 --> 00:51:23,739
[SPEAKER_00] Odlazimo s tako proročkom, teškom riječi

1348
00:51:23,739 --> 00:51:25,760
[SPEAKER_00] i znate šta poslije bude

1349
00:51:25,760 --> 00:51:28,139
[SPEAKER_00] nakon što se Šaul ispričavao bezuspješno.

1350
00:51:28,139 --> 00:51:29,800
[SPEAKER_00] Šaul ga moli

1351
00:51:29,800 --> 00:51:32,699
[SPEAKER_00] da ipak s njim dođe pred glavare.

1352
00:51:32,699 --> 00:51:35,739
[SPEAKER_00] Da mu iskaze čast.

1353
00:51:35,739 --> 00:51:37,860
[SPEAKER_00] I samo ide s njim.

1354
00:51:44,820 --> 00:51:48,400
[SPEAKER_00] Dobar glas.

1355
00:51:48,400 --> 00:51:53,239
[SPEAKER_00] Tako ćemo imati dobar glas mi, katolici.

1356
00:51:53,239 --> 00:51:55,920
[SPEAKER_00] Kad poštojemo one koji su iznad nas.

1357
00:51:55,920 --> 00:52:00,260
[SPEAKER_00] Ne radi nas sami da imamo neke veze, vezice.

1358
00:52:00,260 --> 00:52:03,119
[SPEAKER_00] Nego da se kraljestvo Bože širi.

1359
00:52:06,239 --> 00:52:10,139
[SPEAKER_00] I ovaj citat vodilja gdje Petar kaže

1360
00:52:10,139 --> 00:52:12,559
[SPEAKER_00] kralja častite.

1361
00:52:12,559 --> 00:52:16,619
[SPEAKER_00] Morate znat da je tad kralj bio njegov sin,

1362
00:52:16,619 --> 00:52:18,139
[SPEAKER_00] Herodov sin, Heroda Gripa.

1363
00:52:18,139 --> 00:52:21,420
[SPEAKER_00] I on je bio kralj koji je progonio kršćane.

1364
00:52:21,420 --> 00:52:23,460
[SPEAKER_00] On je bio kralj koji je ubio Jakova,

1365
00:52:23,460 --> 00:52:24,780
[SPEAKER_00] brata Ivanova.

1366
00:52:24,780 --> 00:52:29,019
[SPEAKER_00] On je bio kralj koji je stavio Petra u tamnicu

1367
00:52:29,019 --> 00:52:30,320
[SPEAKER_00] i htio ga pogubiti,

1368
00:52:30,320 --> 00:52:34,179
[SPEAKER_00] ali su poslušni i vjerni kršćani molili.

1369
00:52:34,179 --> 00:52:37,320
[SPEAKER_00] I on je bio čudesno izbavljen.

1370
00:52:37,320 --> 00:52:42,139
[SPEAKER_00] Ali Bog je dosudio njemu

1371
00:52:42,139 --> 00:52:43,699
[SPEAKER_00] zbog poslušnosti crkve.

1372
00:52:43,699 --> 00:52:47,519
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon toga vidimo da ga Bog kažnjava

1373
00:52:47,519 --> 00:52:48,940
[SPEAKER_00] i Bog se sudi s njim.

1374
00:52:48,940 --> 00:52:52,019
[SPEAKER_00] Jer on održi govor.

1375
00:52:52,019 --> 00:52:53,900
[SPEAKER_00] Svi kažu ovo je božanski,

1376
00:52:53,900 --> 00:52:55,719
[SPEAKER_00] ovo su Božje riječi.

1377
00:52:55,719 --> 00:52:57,820
[SPEAKER_00] I budući da on svom srcu nije dao

1378
00:52:57,820 --> 00:52:59,300
[SPEAKER_00] hvalu Bogu za taj govor.

1379
00:52:59,300 --> 00:53:01,880
[SPEAKER_00] Piše da je u trenu

1380
00:53:01,880 --> 00:53:04,619
[SPEAKER_00] pao mrtav.

1381
00:53:04,619 --> 00:53:08,320
[SPEAKER_00] Srvi su ga iznutra pojeli.

1382
00:53:08,320 --> 00:53:11,059
[SPEAKER_00] To se dogodilo Herodu u gripi.

1383
00:53:11,059 --> 00:53:12,460
[SPEAKER_00] Bog se s njima obračunava.

1384
00:53:12,460 --> 00:53:17,760
[SPEAKER_00] Bog postavlja i one loše

1385
00:53:17,760 --> 00:53:18,840
[SPEAKER_00] i pokvarane vladare.

1386
00:53:18,840 --> 00:53:20,840
[SPEAKER_00] Na bukodonozora

1387
00:53:20,840 --> 00:53:24,079
[SPEAKER_00] koji je tlačio Izraelce godinama

1388
00:53:24,079 --> 00:53:25,099
[SPEAKER_00] zove

1389
00:53:25,099 --> 00:53:26,800
[SPEAKER_00] pozovi moga slugu.

1390
00:53:27,820 --> 00:53:30,940
[SPEAKER_00] toga moramo biti svjesni.

1391
00:53:30,940 --> 00:53:33,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ali duboko u srcu,

1392
00:53:33,019 --> 00:53:34,019
[SPEAKER_00] ne samo ovako izvana.

1393
00:53:34,019 --> 00:53:36,360
[SPEAKER_00] U svojem djelovanju,

1394
00:53:36,360 --> 00:53:38,380
[SPEAKER_00] svojim mislima,

1395
00:53:38,380 --> 00:53:39,199
[SPEAKER_00] riječima,

1396
00:53:39,199 --> 00:53:40,300
[SPEAKER_00] pazit.

1397
00:53:40,300 --> 00:53:41,619
[SPEAKER_00] Da damo čast

1398
00:53:41,619 --> 00:53:43,300
[SPEAKER_00] društvenim voditeljima.

1399
00:53:43,300 --> 00:53:47,300
[SPEAKER_00] Odnosno državnim.

1400
00:53:47,300 --> 00:53:49,639
[SPEAKER_00] A sad prelazimo na

1401
00:53:49,639 --> 00:53:51,300
[SPEAKER_00] društvene.

1402
00:53:51,300 --> 00:53:53,460
[SPEAKER_00] To su

1403
00:53:53,460 --> 00:53:55,500
[SPEAKER_00] naši poslodavci, učitelji.

1404
00:53:56,420 --> 00:53:57,340
[SPEAKER_00] Znate šta, iskreno,

1405
00:53:57,340 --> 00:53:59,579
[SPEAKER_00] kad pričam ovako s mladima,

1406
00:53:59,579 --> 00:54:01,539
[SPEAKER_00] posljedno znaših zajednica,

1407
00:54:01,539 --> 00:54:03,679
[SPEAKER_00] i kad pričam, ne znam,

1408
00:54:03,679 --> 00:54:04,820
[SPEAKER_00] fakultetu u školi,

1409
00:54:04,820 --> 00:54:06,860
[SPEAKER_00] rijetko kad čujem dobru riječ

1410
00:54:06,860 --> 00:54:07,920
[SPEAKER_00] o profesoru i učitelju.

1411
00:54:07,920 --> 00:54:08,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ali čujem.

1412
00:54:08,559 --> 00:54:11,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kad se priča o poslodavcima,

1413
00:54:11,500 --> 00:54:13,699
[SPEAKER_00] nisam čuo dugo jednu dobru.

1414
00:54:15,699 --> 00:54:17,619
[SPEAKER_00] A šta Pavao piše?

1415
00:54:17,619 --> 00:54:19,159
[SPEAKER_00] Hoću vam to pročitati.

1416
00:54:19,159 --> 00:54:24,059
[SPEAKER_00] U Efežanima.

1417
00:54:26,340 --> 00:54:29,320
[SPEAKER_00] Tad je još bilo legalno imat roba.

1418
00:54:29,320 --> 00:54:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] On kaže, robovi,

1419
00:54:31,000 --> 00:54:33,179
[SPEAKER_00] slušajte svoje zemaljske gospodare,

1420
00:54:33,179 --> 00:54:34,059
[SPEAKER_00] kao Krista,

1421
00:54:34,059 --> 00:54:35,960
[SPEAKER_00] sa strahom i trepetom,

1422
00:54:35,960 --> 00:54:37,460
[SPEAKER_00] u jednostavnosti srca.

1423
00:54:37,460 --> 00:54:40,099
[SPEAKER_00] Možda nismo robovi,

1424
00:54:40,099 --> 00:54:41,840
[SPEAKER_00] jer imamo pravo dati otkaz,

1425
00:54:41,840 --> 00:54:42,840
[SPEAKER_00] ali ti hosam sati,

1426
00:54:42,840 --> 00:54:44,019
[SPEAKER_00] kad ti radiš za poslodavca,

1427
00:54:44,019 --> 00:54:45,380
[SPEAKER_00] on je tebi zemaljski gospodar.

1428
00:54:45,460 --> 00:54:47,639
[SPEAKER_00] ti moraš raditi ono što on kaže,

1429
00:54:47,639 --> 00:54:48,900
[SPEAKER_00] inače nećeš dobiti plaću.

1430
00:54:48,900 --> 00:54:50,800
[SPEAKER_00] Ne na oko,

1431
00:54:50,800 --> 00:54:54,559
[SPEAKER_00] kao oni koji se ulaguju ljudima,

1432
00:54:54,559 --> 00:54:56,019
[SPEAKER_00] nego kao sluge Kristove

1433
00:54:56,019 --> 00:54:57,639
[SPEAKER_00] koji izdušno vrše volju Božju.

1434
